  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bc7\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0bc7\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bc1 - 2 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Nightclub shooting in Norway kills 2",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two people have been killed in a shooting at a nightclub in Norway.",
        "A shooting has erupted at a nightclub in the Norwegian capital Oslo today.",
        "Two people at the nightclub were killed in the shooting. Another 10 people were seriously injured.",
        "Police rushed to the spot, arrested the fugitive and are investigating.",
        "Police are investigating the man arrested for the cause of the shooting. Police have not released any information about the details of the person arrested.",
        "The shooting at a nightclub in Norway has caused a stir in the region."
      ],
